<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT1.1">
<l>koṅkai tiraṅki narampe ḻuntu kuṇṭukaṇ veṇpaṟ kuḻiva yiṟṟup</l>
<l>paṅki civantiru paṟkaḷ nīṇṭu paraṭuyar nīḷkaṇaik kālōr peṇpēy</l>
<l>taṅki yalaṟi yulaṟu kāṭṭiṟ ṟāḻcaṭai yeṭṭut ticaiyum vīci</l>
<l>yaṅkaṅ kuḷirntaṉa lāṭu meṅka ḷappa ṉiṭantiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where our father dances with fire, [his] limbs cooling, flinging [his] hanging matted hair in all the eight directions,</l>
<l>in the cremation ground where one female demon stays [and] weeps [and] howls,</l>
<l>[her] breasts shrunk, veins risen, deep eyes, white teeth, hollow belly, hair reddened,</l>
<l>two teeth elongated, ankles high, long round legs, is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
